==評價==
《Car & Drive》杂志、<ref name="candd">{{cite web |url=http://www.caranddriver.com/bestcars/7579/10best-cars-honda-s2000.html |title=Honda S2000 |work=Car and Driver |accessdate=2006-09-19 |archive-date=2007-10-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20071019030331/http://www.caranddriver.com/bestcars/7579/10best-cars-honda-s2000.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>《Car》杂志、《洛杉磯時報》，《Road & Track》对S2000均给予了一致好評。其中突出的優點是引擎的高效率輸出，各方面性能的平衡性，以及手感十分順暢的手動變速箱等。<ref name="autoexpress">{{cite web |url=http://www.autoexpress.co.uk/news/autoexpressnews/65609/driver_power_2006_japanese_top_the_big_report.html |title=Driver Power 2006: Japanese top the big report! |work=AutoExpress |accessdate=2006-09-19 |archive-date=2012-02-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120226211635/http://www.autoexpress.co.uk/news/autoexpressnews/65609/driver_power_2006_japanese_top_the_big_report.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="topgear">{{cite web |url=http://www.topgear.com/content/features/stories/2005/11/stories/01/1.html |title=Top Gear Survey 2005 - the results |work=Top Gear |accessdate=2006-06-19 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20060706221359/http://www.topgear.com/content/features/stories/2005/11/stories/01/1.html |archivedate=2006-07-06 }}</ref>

